  <!-- Section 1: Executive Summary -->
  <h1>1. Executive Summary</h1>
  <p>
    The <strong>Mahanadi Coalfields Limited (MCL) Internship Management Portal</strong> is a high-performance web application engineered to centralize, automate, and secure the end-to-end administration of student interns across all operational Areas and Headquarters of MCL.
  </p>
  <p>
    Historically, processing LOR referrals, managing student files, collecting attendance logs, and issuing training certificates involved heavy manual work across several offices, creating data delays and security concerns. The portal resolves these inefficiencies by establishing a secure digital platform accessible by Employees, local Area Training Officers, Mentors, and Students.
  </p>
  <div class="callout">
    <p>🎯 Key Business Deliverable: An administrative workspace that automates credential provisioning, attendance range validation, logbook oversight, and prints certificates with transparent logos, digital signatures, and database-matched validation QR codes.</p>
  </div>

